. military apparatus, American forces are critically overextended and ever threatened by the simmering resistance each new &quot;victory&quot; breeds. Though America is still the land of unprecedented prosperity, economic breakdown looms, the consequence of gargantuan military costs, exploitative trade and investment relations with developing countries, and record-breaking deficits.\n\nA clear and prophetic examination, Dilemmas of Domination reveals a not-too-distant future in which the empire\'s hidden weaknesses will yield fatal challenges to American omnipotence.\n\n&quot;With unsentimental clarity, Walden Bello speaks the truth about American empire and why it is doomed by its own contradictions.&quot; —William Greider, author of The Soul of Capitalism<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"17126742835901950511\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'34_book_244719\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"RWu2Tyjz/lFLWbO7qzMDtRHQD88uezm7uj5EXWO9fgMIfoBlpDUnOLwOhkGma291Y7aJagOAq9iqfUKeYGYQwQ==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"244719\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"34_book_244719\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"existing_review\" id=\"existing_review\" value=\"false\" class=\"wtrExisting\" />\n<input 